7
00:01:08,480 --> 00:01:09,720
Then, Sinian and I...

8
00:01:09,720 --> 00:01:11,280
surely won't have this problem.

9
00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:12,280
Our engagement...

10
00:01:12,280 --> 00:01:14,560
