11
00:01:14,560 --> 00:01:16,289
It's exactly what I wished for.

12
00:01:16,880 --> 00:01:19,000
The Cold family and the Lin family are well-matched.

13
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:21,480
It's naturally different from us common folk.

14
00:01:21,480 --> 00:01:23,240
If we're talking about sincerity...

15
00:01:23,240 --> 00:01:24,500
