20
00:01:59,280 --> 00:02:00,080
Sinian,

21
00:02:00,600 --> 00:02:01,960
I'm a bit cold too.

22
00:02:04,240 --> 00:02:05,970
Zichuan, give her the clothes.

23
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:16,520
Chen Qingyan can't stay.

24
00:02:25,040 --> 00:02:26,770
Dr. Chen, you're finally here.

25
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:27,960
I'm sorry.

26
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:29,520
I was delayed by something earlier.

27
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:31,040
Miss Lin, where are you feeling unwell?

28
00:02:31,040 --> 00:02:32,500
I don't feel well all over.

29
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:35,640
I'm dizzy, my vision is blurry, and I feel weak all over.

30
00:02:35,640 --> 00:02:37,700
Thank you for your trouble, Dr. Chen.

31
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:39,400
Please extend your arm.

32
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:40,660
I'll check your pulse.

33
00:02:44,200 --> 00:02:45,400
Your pulse is steady.

34
00:02:45,600 --> 00:02:47,240
Your qi and blood are balanced.

35
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:48,680
Your breathing is extended.

36
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:49,810
Your spirit is good.

37
00:02:50,880 --> 00:02:52,140
She's faking illness.

38
00:02:55,160 --> 00:02:57,320
Have you found out what's wrong with me?

39
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:59,079
Miss Lin, there's nothing seriously wrong with your body.

40
00:02:59,079 --> 00:03:00,410
You just need some rest.

41
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:02,360
I see.

42
00:03:03,320 --> 00:03:04,850
Dr. Chen is young after all.

43
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:06,280
Some complex conditions

44
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:08,010
are normal to be undetectable.

45
00:03:08,160 --> 00:03:09,800
Miss Lin, if you're worried,

46
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:11,200
you can ask the Governor

47
00:03:11,200 --> 00:03:12,880
to find a famous doctor

48
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:14,530
to examine you thoroughly.

49
00:03:15,720 --> 00:03:17,579
Dr. Chen, you've misunderstood.

50
00:03:17,720 --> 00:03:19,800
You are, after all, someone Si Nian values.

51
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:21,660
I really can't trust anyone else.

52
00:03:22,440 --> 00:03:23,900
I only trust you, Dr. Chen.

53
00:03:25,640 --> 00:03:27,840
Thank you for your personal attention.

54
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:56,100
What medicine is this?

55
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:59,460
It's for soothing the liver and relieving depression.

56
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:04,000
