58
00:04:10,600 --> 00:04:11,730
What's wrong, Miss?

59
00:04:13,880 --> 00:04:14,740
It's so bitter.

60
00:04:15,720 --> 00:04:17,250
What kind of doctor are you?

61
00:04:17,279 --> 00:04:18,720
This medicine is both hot and bitter.

62
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:19,839
Who can drink this?

63
00:04:20,519 --> 00:04:22,360
Don't you want our Miss to get better soon?

64
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:23,480
just say it straight.

65
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:24,680
You're full of bad intentions.

66
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:26,360
afraid others can't see through you?

67
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:28,080
You, go and brew a new batch right now.

68
00:04:28,080 --> 00:04:29,840
I am Leng Sinian's personal doctor.

69
00:04:29,840 --> 00:04:31,000
