71
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:34,780
you've succeeded.

72
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:36,330
I won't stay any longer.

73
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:38,680
This illness of yours, from who knows where,

74
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:40,680
go find whoever you want to treat it.

75
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:43,000
You stop right there!

76
00:05:14,280 --> 00:05:15,480
Is that Si Nian?

77
00:05:23,960 --> 00:05:24,680
Don't move.

78
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:25,760
Let me go.

79
00:05:26,520 --> 00:05:27,920
The more you struggle, the more I like it.

80
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:28,520
Help!

81
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:34,080
Let me go.

82
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:45,560
