83
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:46,520
Keep screaming.

84
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:52,050
Are you alright?

85
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:54,650
Why are you here?

86
00:05:56,640 --> 00:05:58,000
In the middle of the night,

87
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,860
I saw him sneaking into your room,

88
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:01,370
