92
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:39,360
Dr. Chen?

93
00:06:46,200 --> 00:06:47,159
Dr. Chen.

94
00:06:47,520 --> 00:06:48,760
What are you doing?

95
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:54,620
Miss Lin, why did you suddenly come here?

96
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:56,320
I heard some noise outside.

97
00:06:56,320 --> 00:06:57,320
I thought something had happened.

98
00:06:57,320 --> 00:06:58,520
so I rushed over here.

99
00:06:58,640 --> 00:06:59,700
I didn't expect...

100
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:01,640
I'm sorry for the disturbance.

101
00:07:01,640 --> 00:07:02,440
It's alright.

102
00:07:03,200 --> 00:07:04,880
I should really thank you, Miss Lin.

103
00:07:04,880 --> 00:07:06,740
Thanks to you for sending me a man.

104
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:10,450
Dr. Chen, have you misunderstood something?

105
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:11,850
Misunderstanding?

106
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:14,440
This morning, I had just left Miss Lin's room.

107
00:07:14,440 --> 00:07:16,200
when I was knocked unconscious.

108
00:07:16,200 --> 00:07:18,720
