109
00:07:18,720 --> 00:07:19,480
Dr. Chen,

110
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:21,360
you are the Governor's personal physician.

111
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:22,840
Even if you were meeting a man in private here,

112
00:07:22,840 --> 00:07:23,640
and I happened to catch you,

113
00:07:23,640 --> 00:07:25,840
you don't need to sling mud at me, do you?

114
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:29,160
Miss Lin is indeed straightforward.

115
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:29,880
However,

116
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:32,140
your plan should have failed.

117
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:39,960
Si Nian.

118
00:07:40,960 --> 00:07:41,840
Why is it you?

119
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:43,840
Why can't it be me?

120
00:07:45,320 --> 00:07:47,520
So you're the one who wanted to harm her.

121
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:50,050
How come even you don't believe me?

122
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:53,050
Shouldn't you be the one who understands me the most?

123
00:07:54,400 --> 00:07:55,200
I once

124
00:07:55,960 --> 00:07:56,840
thought so too.

125
00:07:58,240 --> 00:07:59,000
Come out!

126
00:08:04,520 --> 00:08:04,980
Tell me,

127
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:06,760
did she send you here?

128
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:11,760
You'd better tell the truth.

129
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:13,640
Otherwise, you know I

130
00:08:14,280 --> 00:08:15,880
I understand, I understand.

131
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:18,240
Yes, yes.

132
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:18,840
It was me.

133
00:08:22,760 --> 00:08:23,820
I asked him to come.

134
00:08:26,520 --> 00:08:27,520
You did it.

135
00:08:29,560 --> 00:08:31,760
Zhiyao grew up with us since childhood.

136
00:08:32,520 --> 00:08:34,039
But these days, you've been constantly

137
00:08:34,039 --> 00:08:35,240
favoring this woman.

138
00:08:35,559 --> 00:08:38,020
Naturally, I won't let her have an easy time.

139
00:08:43,120 --> 00:08:44,920
Today, whether it was you or not,

140
00:08:45,640 --> 00:08:47,280
or anyone else,

141
00:08:48,400 --> 00:08:49,680
whoever has any ill intentions

142
00:08:49,680 --> 00:08:51,010
towards Dr. Chen again,

143
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:52,980
there's only one path:

144
00:08:54,520 --> 00:08:55,120
Death.

145
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:01,200
Qingyan,

146
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:03,600
do you have anything else to say?

147
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:09,120
Let's forget about today's incident.

148
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:10,160
Miss Lin,

149
00:09:10,800 --> 00:09:12,200
you've given me a hard time before,

150
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:12,880
humiliated me,

151
00:09:12,880 --> 00:09:14,410
I won't hold it against you.

152
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:17,280
But if something like this happens again in the future,

153
00:09:17,280 --> 00:09:19,210
I definitely won't show any mercy.

154
00:09:22,520 --> 00:09:23,250
Come with me.

155
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:33,860
Don't move.

156
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:44,660
You were troubled before.

157
00:09:45,040 --> 00:09:46,300
why didn't you tell me?

158
00:09:46,680 --> 00:09:47,880
I'm just your doctor.

159
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:49,720
