184
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:26,080
Indeed, he's a child born of a concubine.

185
00:11:26,080 --> 00:11:27,920
How could he compare to the young commander born of the first wife?

186
00:11:27,920 --> 00:11:28,760
That's right.

187
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:31,890
No wonder he's not as good as his brother at anything.

188
00:11:32,400 --> 00:11:33,040
Zi Chuan,

189
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:34,720
that article you revised for me

190
